000100******************************************************************        
000200*                         RVWS102                                *        
000300*                                                                *        
000400*   THIS IS THE APPLICATION SPECIFIC COMMUNICATION AREA FOR      *        
000500*   THE REQ RA PRINT PROGRAM RVKCS112.  PROGRAMS WHICH PASS DATA *        
000600*   TO RVKCS112 WILL USE THIS AREA.                              *        
000700*                                                                *        
000800*   THE PROGRAM MUST FILL IN THE REQUEST FOR RETURN AUTH NUMBER, *        
000900*   THE PRINTER DESTINATION, BUYER NAME, DEFECT ORDER ITEM STATUS*        
001000*   AND THE PROGRAM NAME WHICH SENT THE INFORMATION.             *        
001100*   THE DESTINATION MUST POINT TO A VALID PRINTRONIX PRINTER     *        
001200*                                                                *        
001300*   LENGTH:  56 BYTES                                            *        
001400******************************************************************        
001500 01  RV102-SPECIFIC-COMMAREA.                                             
001600     05  RV102-DEFECT-ORDER-NBR      PIC S9(12)V   VALUE +0               
001700                                                   COMP-3.                
001800     05  RV102-PRINTER-DEST          PIC  X(08)    VALUE SPACES.          
001900     05  RV102-BUYER-NAME            PIC  X(15)    VALUE SPACES.          
002000     05  RV102-DFCTOR-ITEM-STATUS    PIC S9(04)V   VALUE +0               
002100                                                   COMP-3.                
002200     05  RV102-PROGRAM-NAME          PIC  X(8)     VALUE SPACES.          
002300     05  RV102-OPER-UNT-ID           PIC  9(04)    VALUE ZEROS.           
002400     05  RV102-MKOUT-ORD-ID          PIC S9(11)V   VALUE +0               
002500                                                   COMP-3.                
002600     05  RV102-USERID                PIC  X(8)     VALUE SPACES.          
